Anambra Election Inec Result Update: APGA emeriwala na 4 n'ime okpuruọchịchị 21 n'Anambra
Dịka o si aga, Returning Officer onye na-ewega mpụtara ntuliaka e mere ekwupụtala na o nweghị ntuliaka e mere n'Ihiala n'ụbọchị 6 Nọvemba.

Cheta na ụlọọrụ Independent National Electoral Commission, INEC amalitela nchịkọta mpụtara ntuliaka ọkwa gọvanọ Anambra steeti n'ogogo steeti n'ụtụtụ Sọnde dịka a malitere ịchịkọta nke wọọdụ na okpuru ọchịchị n'ụbọchị Satọde.
Nwalee ma ị ma gọvanọ ndị chiburu Anambra steeti
Anambra election result: Inec ekwupụtala onyeisi nchịkọta mpụtara ntuliaka Anambra bụ Ọkammụta Florence Banku Obi
Nke a na-abịa dịka Inec dọtịkwuru oge ntuliaka ruo taa bụ Sọnde iji nye ndị igwe ndenye aha BVAS (nke Inec ji arụ ọrụ) ekweghi mee ntuliaka ụnyaahụ, ohere ịtụ vootu.
Dịka Inec si depụta. ihe ọ na-ewe iji kpọpụta mpụtara onye meriri na ntuliaka onyeisiala maọbụ nke gọvano bụ onye a kachasị tunyere vootu.
Nke a pụtara na onye ahụ ga-emeriri otu ụzọ n'ụzo anọ ndị niile a turu vootu n'ụzọ abụo n'ime ụzọ atọ nke steeti niile dị na Naịjirịa maọbụ okpuruọchịchị  dị na steeti.
Ebe a ka ị ga-ahụ mpụtara vootu niile a tụrụ n'Anambra steeti, nke Bekee kpọrọ "Anambra election update".
Chief "returning officer" nke Orumba Noọtụ bụ dkt Michael Otu ekwuola na amanyere ya amanye ibianye aka n'akwụkwọ e ji agụkọ vootu.
Ọkammụta Florence Obi bụ 'electoral officer' nke Anambra gwara ya kọwatụ ihe merenụ.
O kwuru na ndị omekome nakwa ndị uweojii kụrụ ya na osote ya ihe tịnka kụrụ pan n'oge ntụliaka ahụ mere na Nov 7,2021.
Obi gwara ọkammụta Otu ka o gaa depụta mkpesa ahụ n'akwụkwọ.
